'''斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆'''（'''Stephen Wolfram'''，{{bd|1959年|8月29日}}），旧译'''斯蒂芬·沃尔夫雷姆'''，是[[计算机科学|计算机科学]]、[[数学|数学]]、[[理论物理|理论物理]]方面的著名英国科学家<ref>{{cite journal |title=Stephen Wolfram |url=http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=Stephen+Wolfram |publisher=Wolfram Alpha |accessdate=15 May 2012 |journal= |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207234527/http://www.wolframalpha.com/input/?i=Stephen+Wolfram |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |publisher=New Scientist |title=Stephen Wolfram: 'I am an information pack rat' |url=http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg20427381.100-stephen-wolfram-im-an-information-pack-rat.html |accessdate=19 April 2014 |journal= |archive-date=2015-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423101925/http://www.newscientist.com/article/mg20427381.100-stephen-wolfram-im-an-information-pack-rat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他编写了著作《一种新科学》<ref name="scopus">{{Scopus|id=16493873100}}</ref>。同时，他还是著名大学[[伊利诺伊大学厄巴纳-香槟分校|伊利诺伊大学厄巴纳-香槟分校]]的兼职教授<ref>{{cite web |url=https://physics.illinois.edu/people/profile.asp?wolfram |title=adjunct professor in UIUC |accessdate=2015-11-06 |archive-date=2015-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120202841/https://physics.illinois.edu/people/profile.asp?wolfram |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2012年，他成为美国数学协会的院士。<ref>[http://www.ams.org/profession/fellows-list List of Fellows of the American Mathematical Society] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ams.org/profession/fellows-list |date=20190422023001 }}, retrieved 1 September 2013.</ref>

作为商人，他是软件公司[[沃尔夫勒姆研究公司|沃尔夫勒姆研究公司]]的创立者和首席执行官。在公司内部，他是[[数学软件|数学软件]] [[Mathematica|Mathematica]] 和计算型知识引擎 [[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]] 的主要设计师。他近期的工作主要是基于知识的编程，把 Mathematica 编程语言进一步拓展为 [[Wolfram_语言|Wolfram 语言]]。他的相关著作《Wolfram 语言入门》的英文版发行于2015年。在学术上，他以[[粒子物理学|粒子物理学]]、[[元胞自动机|元胞自动机]]、[[宇宙学|宇宙学]]、[[复杂性理论|复杂性理论]]、[[计算机代数系统|计算机代数系统]]上的研究成果闻名于世。他是一名[[左撇子|左撇子]]。

== 早期生活 ==
斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆1959年出生于伦敦，曾先后就读于[[伊顿公学|伊顿公学]]、[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]。他的父亲雨果·沃尔夫勒姆是小说家，母亲西比尔·沃尔夫勒姆是哲学教授。

=== 雨果·沃尔夫勒姆 ===

斯蒂芬的父亲雨果·沃尔夫勒姆（1925 - 2015）出生于德国波鸿市，是一位纺织品制造商，曾担任卢勒克斯公司的常务董事，织物卢勒克斯的制造商，同时也是三本小说的作者。<ref name="Telling a good yarn by Jenny Lunnon">[http://www.oxfordtimes.co.uk/business/profiles/931620.Telling_a_good_yarn/ Telling a good yarn by Jenny Lunnon] {{Wayback|url=http://www.oxfordtimes.co.uk/business/profiles/931620.Telling_a_good_yarn/ |date=20151126042320 }}, Oxford Times, Thursday 21 September 2006.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/24/us/physicist-awarded-genius-prize-finds-reality-in-invisible-world.html |title=PHYSICIST AWARDED 'GENIUS' PRIZE FINDS REALITY IN INVISIBLE WORLD, by GLADWIN HILL, Special to the New York Times, Published: May 24, 1981 |accessdate=2016-03-04 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307215744/http://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/24/us/physicist-awarded-genius-prize-finds-reality-in-invisible-world.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://hgar-srv3.bu.edu/collections/collection?id=123005 Howard Gottlieb Archival Research Center:  Wolfram, Hugo (1925- )] {{Wayback|url=http://hgar-srv3.bu.edu/collections/collection?id=123005 |date=20190601150324 }}: "The Hugo Wolfram collection consists of manuscripts by Wolfram for novels, short stories, and essays."</ref><ref>[https://www.kirkusreviews.com/book-reviews/hugo-wolfram/into-a-neutral-country/ Kirkus review of ''Into a Neutral Country''] {{Wayback|url=https://www.kirkusreviews.com/book-reviews/hugo-wolfram/into-a-neutral-country/ |date=20160304060748 }}, 1969</ref> 雨果出生于德国，于1933年移民到英格兰。<ref>[http://www.juedischeliteraturwestfalen.de/index.php?valex=101&vArticle=1&author_id=00000308&id=1 Hugo Wolfram. 1925- ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.juedischeliteraturwestfalen.de/index.php?valex=101&vArticle=1&author_id=00000308&id=1 |date=20151123085830 }}, Jüdische Schriftstellerinnen und Schriftsteller in Westfalen.</ref> 当[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]爆发后，年轻的雨果在15岁时离开学校，后来发现，因为他被视为一个很难找到一份工作“敌国侨民”。作为一个成年人，他参加了[[哲学|哲学]]和[[心理学|心理学]]函授课程。<ref name="Telling a good yarn by Jenny Lunnon"/>

=== 西比尔·沃尔夫勒姆 ===
斯蒂芬的母亲西比尔·沃尔夫勒姆(1931-1993，出生西比尔米施)从1964年到1993年任[[牛津大学|牛津大学]]玛格丽特夫人学堂的院士和讲师。她出版了两本著作''Philosophical Logic: an Introduction'' (1989)<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=HSXJBQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=sybil+wolfram+philosophy&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiMteWqhqzJAhWJdD4KHaBODBcQ6AEIJDAA#v=onepage&q=sybil%20wolfram%20philosophy&f=false ''Philosophical Logic: An Introduction'' by Sybil Wolfram] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=HSXJBQAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=sybil+wolfram+philosophy&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiMteWqhqzJAhWJdD4KHaBODBcQ6AEIJDAA#v=onepage&q=sybil%20wolfram%20philosophy&f=false |date=20160624044748 }} on Google Books.</ref> 和 ''In-laws and Outlaws: Kinship and Marriage in England'' (1987).<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=yZoOAAAAQAAJ&dq=sybil+wolfram&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiZr5ewh6zJAhUDPz4KHd0XAUkQ6AEIIzAB In-laws and Outlaws: Kinship and Marriage in England by Sybil Wolfram] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yZoOAAAAQAAJ&dq=sybil+wolfram&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiZr5ewh6zJAhUDPz4KHd0XAUkQ6AEIIzAB |date=20160609174547 }} on Google Books.</ref><ref name="levy1006">{{cite news | url=http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/10.06/wolfram_pr.html | title=The Man Who Cracked The Code to Everything ... | accessdate=2015-03-03 | author=Levy, Steven | issue=10.06 | publisher=Wired | archive-date=2014-03-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314121909/http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/10.06/wolfram_pr.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 她翻译了由Claude Lévi-Strauss著作的 ''La pensée sauvage'' (''The Savage Mind'')，但是后来否认了翻译。<ref>[http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1525/aa.1967.69.1.02a00160/epdf Letter to the Editor] {{Wayback|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1525/aa.1967.69.1.02a00160/epdf |date=20160305145122 }}, ''American Anthropologist'', February, 1967.</ref><ref>''Times Literary Supplement'', October 29, 2008. "The century of Claude Lévi-Strauss: How the great anthropologist, now approaching his 100th birthday, has earned a place in the prestigious Pléiade library", by Patrick Wilcken.</ref> 她是犯罪学家和心理分析学家凯特·弗里德兰德 (1902-1949)<ref>[https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Psycho_Analytical_Approach_to_Juveni.html?id=MU1U1M8F3ekC ''The Psycho-Analytical Approach to Juvenile Delinquency: Theory, Case Studies, Treatment'' by Kate Friedlander (1947)] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Psycho_Analytical_Approach_to_Juveni.html?id=MU1U1M8F3ekC |date=20160430080436 }} on Google Books.</ref> 和物理学家 Walter Misch (1889-1943) 的女儿。在1933年德国国会大厦火灾后，她从德国柏林随父母和犹太精神分析学家 Paula Heimann(1899–1982)移民到英国。<ref name="jstor.org">Smith, M. E.. (1993). Obituary. Anthropology Today, 9(6), 22–22. Retrieved from http://www.jstor.org/stable/2783224 {{Wayback|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/2783224 |date=20151126074508 }}</ref><ref>[https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/judaica/ejud_0002_0007_0_06853.html FRIEDLANDER, KATE in Jewish Virtual Library] {{Wayback|url=https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/judaica/ejud_0002_0007_0_06853.html |date=20160304102009 }}.</ref><ref>[http://www.psychoanalytikerinnen.de/greatbritain_biographies.html#Friedlaender Kate Friedländer née Frankl (1902-1949)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.psychoanalytikerinnen.de/greatbritain_biographies.html#Friedlaender |date=20151126043727 }}, Psychoanalytikerinnen. Biografisches Lexikon.</ref>

== 家庭 ==
他的妻子是一位[[数学家|数学家]]，他们有4个孩子。

== 教育和早期经历 ==
童年时期，沃尔夫勒姆一开始学业上并不顺利，在学习算术上遇到了困难。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/24/us/physicist-awarded-genius-prize-finds-reality-in-invisible-world.html  PHYSICIST AWARDED 'GENIUS' PRIZE FINDS REALITY IN INVISIBLE WORLD, by GLADWIN HILL, Special to the New York Times, Published: May 24, 1981] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1981/05/24/us/physicist-awarded-genius-prize-finds-reality-in-invisible-world.html |date=20160307215744 }}: "''When I first went to school, they thought I was behind,'' he says, ''because I didn't want to read the silly books they gave us. And I never was able to do arithmetic.'' It was when he got into higher mathematics, such as calculus, he says, that he realized there was an invisible world that he wanted to explore."</ref> 12岁时，他编写了一部关于物理的字典。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/ConciseDirectoryOfPhysics.pdf|title=Concise Directory of Physics|year=1972|author=S. Wolfram|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2013-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908140219/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/ConciseDirectoryOfPhysics.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 13岁至14岁之间，他编写了3本关于粒子物理的书籍。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/PhysicsOfSubatomicParticles.pdf|title=The Physics of Subatomic Particles|year=1973|author=S. Wolfram|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2011-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615081429/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/PhysicsOfSubatomicParticles.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/IntroductionToTheWeakInteractionVolumeOne.pdf|title=Introduction to the Weak Interaction|volume=1|year=1974|author=S. Wolfram|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2013-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922181314/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/IntroductionToTheWeakInteractionVolumeOne.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/IntroductionToTheWeakInteractionVolumeTwo.pdf|title=Introduction to the Weak Interaction|volume=2|year=1974|author=S. Wolfram|access-date=2016-03-24|archive-date=2013-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908141054/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/books/unpublished/IntroductionToTheWeakInteractionVolumeTwo.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 它们没有发表。斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆15岁时发表第一篇科学论文，17岁进入牛津大学学习；20岁时获得[[加州理工學院|加州理工學院]][[理论物理|理论物理]]博士学位，22岁获得[[麦克阿瑟奖|麦克阿瑟奖]]，23岁时创立[[复杂系统|复杂系统]]研究（complex systems research）领域，27岁时开发[[Mathematica|Mathematica]]软件，创立了斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆公司，从事Mathematica以及其他数学软件、电脑软件的开发和发行。43岁时出版《[[一种新科学|一种新科学]]》。其中，Mathematica及相关产品同时获得了技术与商业上的巨大成功，成为支撑斯蒂芬·沃尔夫勒姆公司的旗舰产品。

=== 粒子物理 ===
沃尔夫勒姆从小就是个神童。15岁时，他开始在应用[[量子场论|量子场论]]与[[粒子物理|粒子物理]]方面的研究和发表科学论文。课题包括物质产生和湮灭的基本相互作用、基本粒子和电流、强子和轻子物理、部分子模型，发表在专业的同行评议的科学期刊，包括Nuclear Physics B、Australian Journal of Physics、Nuovo Cimento 和 Physical Review D<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/articles/particle/ |title=Stephen Wolfram: Articles on Particle Physics |accessdate=2016-03-24 |archive-date=2013-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007121048/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/publications/articles/particle/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

沃尔弗拉姆18岁时独立工作在重夸克产生方面<ref name="bio">{{Cite journal |last1 = Giles|first1 = J.|title = Stephen Wolfram: What kind of science is this?|doi = 10.1038/417216a|journal = Nature|volume = 417|issue = 6886|pages = 216–218|year = 2002|pmid = 12015565|pmc = }}</ref>，发表了一篇引用率很高的论文以及另外九篇论文{{r|levy1006}}，并继续研究，二十岁出头就在粒子物理学方面发表多篇论文。他与杰弗里C.福克斯的强相互作用理论仍在实验粒子物理学中使用<ref name="observables">{{Cite journal |last1=Fox |first1=G. |last2=Wolfram |first2=S. |doi=10.1103/PhysRevLett.41.1581 |title=Observables for the Analysis of Event Shapes in e^{+}e^{-} Annihilation and Other Processes |journal=Physical Review Letters |volume=41 |issue=23 |pages=1581 |year=1978 |pmid= |pmc= }}</ref>。

他在伊顿公​​学接受教育，但在1976年进入圣约翰学院<ref>{{cite web |title=[A Speech for (High-School) Graduates] by Stephen Wolfram a commencement speech for Stanford Online High School |url=http://blog.stephenwolfram.com/2014/06/a-speech-for-high-school-graduates/ |website=StephenWolfram.com |date=June 9, 2014 |quote="You know, as it happens, I myself never officially graduated from high school, and this is actually the first high school graduation I’ve ever been to." |accessdate=2016-03-24 |archive-date=2016-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105205438/http://blog.stephenwolfram.com/2014/06/a-speech-for-high-school-graduates/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，17岁进入牛津大学，但发现课堂“awful”{{r|levy1006}} ，因此1978年未获得学位就离开<ref>''[https://books.google.com/books?id=bbN-6aDFrrAC&lpg=PA151&ots=BhcxLgDQ8v&dq=murray%20Stephen%20wolfram&pg=PA151#v=onepage&q=murray%20gelman%20STephen%20wolfram&f=false Complexity: A Guided Tour]'' by Melanie Mitchell, 2009, p. 151: “In the early 1980s, Stephen Wolfram, a physicist working at the Institute for Advanced Study in Princeton, became fascinated by cellular automata and the patterns they make. Wolfram is one of those legendary child prodigies people like to tell stories about. Born in London in 1959, Wolfram published his first physics paper at 15. Two years later, in the summer after his first year at Oxford, ...  Wolfram wrote a paper in the field of “quantum chromodynamics” that attracted the attention of Nobel Prize winning physicist Murray Gell-Mann, who invited Wolfram to join his group at Caltech…”</ref>，进入加州理工大学{{r|arndt20020517}}<ref>{{cite news |author=Zoë Corbyn |title=Stephen Wolfram: 'The textbook has never interested me': The British child genius who abandoned physics to devote himself to coding and the cosmos |url=http://www.theguardian.com/science/2014/jun/29/stephen-wolfram-textbook-never-interested-me-wolframalpha |publisher=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |date=28 June 2014 |quote="He entered Oxford University at 17 without A-levels and left around a year later without graduating. He was bored and he had been invited to cross the pond by the prestigious California Institute of Technology (Caltech) to do a PhD. 'I had written a bunch of papers and so was pretty well known by that time,'" |accessdate=2016-03-24 |archive-date=2016-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160409224340/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2014/jun/29/stephen-wolfram-textbook-never-interested-me-wolframalpha |dead-url=no }}</ref>。次年，才20岁的他获得了粒子物理学博士学位<ref name="mathgene">{{MathGenealogy|id=114676}}</ref><ref name="wolframphd">{{cite thesis |degree=PhD |first=Stephen |last=Wolfram |title=Some Topics in Theoretical High-Energy Physics |publisher=California Institute of Technology |date=1980 |url=http://thesis.library.caltech.edu/2597 |authorlink=Stephen Wolfram |access-date=2016-03-24 |archive-date=2016-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160404131641/http://thesis.library.caltech.edu/2597/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的论文答辩委员会由[[理查德·费曼|理查德·费曼]]、Peter Goldreich、Frank J. Sciulli 和 Steven Frautschi组成，并且由Richard D.Field主持<ref>{{cite web |author= |title=Application for Approval of the Degree of Doctor of Philosophy |trans-title=博士学位批准申请书 |url=https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:StephenWolframCalTechThesisApplication.pdf |format=pdf |publisher=[[加州理工学院|加州理工学院]] |language=en |date=1979年11月19日 |accessdate=2016年3月24日 |archive-date=2015年11月26日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126082552/https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:StephenWolframCalTechThesisApplication.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1981年，沃尔弗拉姆获得麦克阿瑟天才奖<ref>{{Cite web |title=About Stephen Wolfram |url=http://www.stephenwolfram.com/about/ |website=stephenwolfram.com |accessdate=2015-10-13 |archive-date=2015-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151023232619/http://www.stephenwolfram.com/about/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在他获得博士后，沃尔弗拉姆在加州理工留校任教，成为麦克阿瑟奖学金最年轻的获得者<ref name="arndt20020517">{{cite news |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/bw/stories/2002-05-16/stephen-wolframs-simple-science |title=Stephen Wolfram's Simple Science |accessdate=20 August 2015 |author=Arndt, Michael |date=17 May 2002 |publisher=BusinessWeek |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303180906/http://www.bloomberg.com/bw/stories/2002-05-16/stephen-wolframs-simple-science |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 相关工作 ==
=== 复杂系统和元胞自动机 ===

1983年，沃尔夫勒姆进入[[普林斯顿大学|普林斯顿大学]]自然科学学院，进行对[[元胞自动机|元胞自动机]]的研究。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Wolfram |first1=S. |doi=10.1007/BF01217347 |title=Computation theory of cellular automata |journal=''Communications in Mathematical Physics'' |volume=96 |pages=15–57 |year=1984 |pmid= |pmc=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Martin |first1=O. |last2=Odlyzko |first2=A. M. |last3=Wolfram |first3=S. |doi=10.1007/BF01223745 |title=Algebraic properties of cellular automata |journal=''Communications in Mathematical Physics |volume=93 |issue=2 |pages=219 |year=1984 |pmid= |pmc= }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Wolfram |first1=S. |title=Cellular automaton fluids 1: Basic theory |doi=10.1007/BF01021083 |journal=''Journal of Statistical Physics'' |volume=45 |issue=3–4 |pages=471–526 |year=1986 |pmid= |pmc=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Wolfram |first1=S. |title=Cellular automata as models of complexity |doi=10.1038/311419a0 |journal=Nature |volume=311 |issue=5985 |pages=419–424 |year=1984 |pmid= |pmc=}}</ref><ref name="automata">{{Cite journal |last1=Wolfram |first1=S. |title=Statistical mechanics of cellular automata |doi=10.1103/RevModPhys.55.601 |journal=''Reviews of Modern Physics'' |volume=55 |issue=3 |pages=601 |year=1983 |pmid= |pmc=}}</ref> 主要使用计算机模拟。他系统性地调查了基本元胞自动机制的类别，并发表了一系列论文，初步构建了 Wolfram 代码的理念，发明了一维元胞自动机的命名系统，并且提出元胞行为复杂性的分类机制。他提出规则 110元胞自动机制可能具有[[图灵完备性|图灵完备性]]。

1980年代中期，沃尔夫勒姆与理查德·费曼一起研究物理过程的仿真。<ref name="DH">{{cite web|url=http://www.kurzweilai.net/articles/art0504.html?printable=1|title=Richard Feynman and The Connection Machine|author=W. Daniel Hillis|publisher=Physics Today|date=February 1989|accessdate=3 November 2006|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090728072503/http://www.kurzweilai.net/articles/art0504.html?printable=1|archivedate=2009年7月28日}}</ref>并且提出复杂系统的场，设立了第一个相关课题的研究机构，[[伊利诺伊大学香槟分校|伊利诺伊大学香槟分校]]的复杂系统研究中心（CCSR），还在1987年创办了《复杂系统》期刊。<ref name="wired.com">{{cite news |url=http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/10.06/wolfram_pr.html |title=The Man Who Cracked The Code to Everything |work=''Wired'' |accessdate=7 April 2012 |archive-date=2014-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314121909/http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/10.06/wolfram_pr.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 符号操作程序 ===
1979年和1981年之间，斯蒂芬领导[[加州理工学院|加州理工学院]]物理系的{{Link-en|计算代数系统|Symbolic Manipulation Program}}（Symbolic Manipulation Program，SMP。即符号操作程序） 项目的开发。

在1981年，斯蒂芬被授予[[麦克阿瑟奖|麦克阿瑟奖]]（MacArthur Fellowship）。1983年，他在国家自然科学学院进一步学习，并进行[[元胞自动机|元胞自动机]]的研究，主要研究计算机模拟。
80年代中期， 斯蒂芬使用[[元胞自动机|元胞自动机]]进行了物理过程的模拟研究。

=== Mathematica ===
1986年，斯蒂芬在[[伊利诺伊大学香槟分校|伊利诺伊大学香槟分校]]建立了复杂系统研究中心，并开始开发计算代数系统Mathematica，第一个版本于1988年发行。在1987年，他与其他合作者共同创建了沃尔夫勒姆研究公司公司进一步开发和推广Mathematica。斯蒂芬现为公司首席股东。

=== 《[[一种新科学|一种新科学]]》 ===
从1992年到2002年期间，他还致力于他的著作《一种新科学》的出版，该书提供了一个非常简单的计算系统的一种新的实证研究。此外，這表明了這些類型系統的基本推論，與傳統數學相比倒是更需要建立模型和瞭解自然的複雜。他的结论是，宇宙是在其本质上都是数字，并可以使用简单的程序机理运行，该机理即元胞自动机描述的基本规律。他预测，在科学界，这种认识将会对物理、化学和生物学和其他一般科学领域，产生重大和革命的影响。这也是该书的命名原因。

=== 通用图灵机 ===
斯蒂芬建立了著名的最简通用图灵机，它具有2个状态和5个颜色。接着，斯蒂芬进行了2,985,984个可能的2态3色图灵机的实证研究。从中，斯蒂芬推断出一种最简通用图灵机。

Stephen宣布把价值25000美元的奖<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.wolfram.com/2007/05/today_we_put_a_prize_on_a_smal.html|title=The Prize Announcement; Looking for the formal proof|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2008-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080719121518/http://blog.wolfram.com/2007/05/today_we_put_a_prize_on_a_smal.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>颁发给提供了某个候选方案是否是通用最简的证明的第一个人或者小组。而Alex Smith，一个年仅20岁的来自英国的本科生宣布已经证明了Stephen的图灵机的全局性，并且获得了该奖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.wolfram.com/2007/10/the_prize_is_won_the_simplest.html|title=The Prize Is Won; The Simplest Universal Turing Machine Is Proved|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2008-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080522124754/http://blog.wolfram.com/2007/10/the_prize_is_won_the_simplest.html|dead-url=yes}} The 24 October entry at Wolfram Research's blog announcing the news.</ref>而计算机科学家Vaughan Pratt后来宣称已经发现该证明推理中的一个错误。对此，Stephen、Smith和其他人与Pratt的推理进行了辩论。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012149.html|title=Stephen Wolfram reply in the FOM list|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2012-07-07|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707112023/http://cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012149.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012162.html|title=Todd Rowland reply to Vaughan Pratt in the FOM list|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2007-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102081203/http://cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012162.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012164.html|title=Alex Smith reply to Vaughan Pratt in the FOM list|accessdate=2010-03-02|archive-date=2007-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071102062100/http://www.cs.nyu.edu/pipermail/fom/2007-October/012164.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 计算知识引擎 ===
2009年3月，斯蒂芬宣布[[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]]的发行。沃尔夫勒姆阿尔法作为一个知识型计算搜索引擎，采用新方法提取信息，并具有易于使用的界面。[[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]]不是一个简单的搜索引擎，因为它不是简单地返回基于查询条件的结果，而且尝试通过计算获得结果来输出。

[[Wolfram_Alpha|Wolfram Alpha]] 是[[微软|微软]]的[[必应|必应]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bing.com/community/site_blogs/b/search/archive/2010/08/10/answering-your-questions-with-bing-and-wolfram-alpha.aspx|title=Answering your questions with Bing and Wolfram Alpha|work="Microsoft's Bing blog"|accessdate=7 April 2012|archive-date=2013-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130216024331/http://www.bing.com/community/site_blogs/b/search/archive/2010/08/10/answering-your-questions-with-bing-and-wolfram-alpha.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.xconomy.com/seattle/2010/01/05/stephen-wolfram-talks-bing-partnership-software-strategy-and-the-future-of-knowledge-computing/ Stephen Wolfram Talks Bing Partnership, Software Strategy, and the Future of Knowledge Computing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.xconomy.com/seattle/2010/01/05/stephen-wolfram-talks-bing-partnership-software-strategy-and-the-future-of-knowledge-computing/ |date=20160304134921 }} by Gregory T. Huang, Xconomy, January 5th, 2010.</ref> 和[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]的[[Siri|Siri]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/siri.html|title=iPhone features|publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple]]|accessdate=7 April 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031064942/http://www.apple.com/iphone/features/siri.html|archive-date=2011-10-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>后台所使用的[[问答系统|问答系统]]之一。
<!---- Wolfram presented a talk at the [[TED_(conference)|TED]] conference in 2010,
<ref>{{Cite journal|first=Steven|last=Levy|publisher=WIRED|title=TED 2010: How to Ace a TED Talk|url=http://www.wired.com/epicenter/2010/02/ted-2010-how-to-ace-a-ted-talk/|date=12 February 2010}}</ref>
<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Stephen Wolfram: Computing a theory of everything|publisher=TED|url=http://www.ted.com/talks/stephen_wolfram_computing_a_theory_of_everything.html|date=February 2010}}</ref> and he was named Speaker of the Event for his 2012 talk at [[SXSW|SXSW]].
